WATCH the video ENTIRELY!!! Thank you! 
----
I did this to set this straight because people are saying Gal Gadot IS attacking Depp. 
Now, this account is large in "friend" or "follower" terms, so its not "troll size." 
This account has 46,000 followers, says that it is "friends" with Gal Gadot, and notes it can speak for her. 
So, it either: 1. Can speak for them 
OR
2. has been grifting followers off Gal Gadot's name for YEARS now.,
------
For those not using Twitter, to put that number into perspective, that's over double the followers I have on Twitter. Celebrities have their own accounts, BUT their friends and/or spokespeople get numbers like that. 
-----
And again, I'm not saying anything pro/con. I'm saying if this is a spokesperson, fair enough. if NOT, then they need to be shut down.
